name: User register in Utest

testSteps.description: Example: {firstName=Juan Pablo, lastName=Guzman Quintero, email=juan97guzman8@gmail.com, month=October, day=15, year=1997, city=Medellín, zip=050024, country=Colombia, computer=Windows, version=10, language=English, cellPhone=Xiaomi, model=Mi 10T Lite 5G, system=Android 11, password=123456789*AbC, confirmPassword=123456789*AbC}

stackTrace.methodName: the user should see the text Welcome to the world's largest community of freelance software testers!

children.description: Given the user wants to register on Utest
Actor opens the https://www.utest.com/

When the user start to complete the differents forms to register
| firstName | lastName | email | month | day | year | city | zip | country | computer | version | language | cellPhone | model | system | password | confirmPassword |
| Juan Pablo | Guzman Quintero | juan97guzman8@gmail.com | October | 15 | 1997 | Medellín | 050024 | Colombia | Windows | 10 | English | Xiaomi | Mi 10T Lite 5G | Android 11 | 123456789*AbC | 123456789*AbC |
Actor start to register
Actor clicks on Button join today
Actor form1 personal
Actor enters 'Juan Pablo' into Input for first name
Actor enters 'Guzman Quintero' into Input for Last name
Actor enters 'juan97guzman8@gmail.com' into Input for email
Actor select October on select the month of birth
Actor select 15 on select the day of birth
Actor select 1997 on select the year of birth
Actor clicks on Button for next form
Actor form2 address
Actor enters 'Medellín' into Input for city
Actor enters '050024' into Input for zip
Actor clicks on where we find the country
Actor enters 'Colombia' into Input for country
Actor clicks on Button form next form devices
Actor form3 tell us
Actor clicks on Computer
Actor enters 'Windows' then hits [ENTER] into Select your computer
Actor clicks on Version
Actor enters '10' then hits [ENTER] into Select version
Actor clicks on Language
Actor enters 'English' then hits [ENTER] into Select language
Actor clicks on Button last step
Actor form4 last step
Actor enters '123456789*AbC' into Input for password
Actor enters '123456789*AbC' into Input for confirm password
Actor clicks on checkbox 2
Actor clicks on checkbox 3
Actor clicks on Button confirm register
Then the user should see the text Welcome to the world's largest community of freelance software testers!
